Country officer Poland and Slovenia

Networking with the Embassies and other useful organisations in Poland and Slovenia was essential for the job. Besides this network abroad I kept contact with the Embassies of Poland and Slovenia in The Hague and with colleague from other Ministries/organisations dealing with Poland and Slovenia.
